{"tid":196990,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[立會倒旗]警方證實拘捕鄭松泰","createTime":"2017-04-11T15:42:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T16:30:56.000Z","uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef752bca5fcd423ba76dfc2fd19067bbf33a1a91","tid":196990,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"警方證實就立法會倒插國旗區旗案拘捕鄭松泰<br />\n11.04.2017 23:14<br />\n<br />\n熱血公民立法會議員鄭松泰，去年十月在立法會會議廳內「倒插國旗區旗」，遭警方起訴侮辱國旗及區旗罪。警方表示，徵詢法律意見後，今日拘捕一名三十三歲男子，正被扣查。鄭松泰晚上在社交網站表示，他在長沙灣被警員邀請前往中區警署進行拘捕手續。<br />\n<br />\n去年十月十九日的立法會會議，原訂安排劉小麗、梁頌恆與游蕙禎宣誓，但建制派杯葛會議離場，在點算法定人數期間，鄭松泰將建制派議員插在桌上的區旗和國旗倒插。"},{"pid":"3590482e7ece2af3ab04187d41b90e59bc70c03a","tid":196990,"uid":6851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"屌 咁你啲反佔中點計<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0bP8KzJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0bP8KzJ.jpg&h=859f0415&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GD68N4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGD68N4g.jpg&h=4cc32406&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n選擇性擇法到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4bef1569f540c61dc99a0723fd18263d454dede","tid":196990,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:08:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa3806c4c43e20e530ea2bbf43c7964bd0c49c0a","tid":196990,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:30:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">熱狗係咪全黨入赤柱都唔政治庇護?<br />\n<br />\n陳云根笑鳩佢地呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"9474a97365aa60a56a11f4d5174c9ac2e4f2640b","tid":196990,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:30:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>說好的勇武抗爭?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n說好了的政治庇護呢?"}]}